{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>School trips are just the worst, aren't they?</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The homesickness, the nausea - nothing ever seems to go right, does it, Sammy?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/extras/Boat.png?t=1735394502\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The path to the adult you\u2019re becoming</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the ship docks, the students prepare to step onto the soft grass of Caelum, a small island many used to lovingly call home; no longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/extras/Island.png?t=1735394502\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> starts with accepting the child who walked before you.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But, above all of that, something worse has been festering here for a long time, and it's begun to manifest in strange ways. The hallucinations will get you first; the bodies drop shortly after.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the role of Sammy, a socially awkward teen forced to face the world on her own as what starts off as an uncomfortable week on a small, secluded island turns into a neverending nightmare of sickness and horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/extras/Ashes.png?t=1735394502\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>'sammy.' is a top-down narrative horror experience about finding yourself.</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/extras/Characters\u00a8.png?t=1735394502\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Explore your surroundings while adhering to your schedule.</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Daytime - During the daytime you get to explore the island. Do what you must.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nighttime -\u00a0 <span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>cadaver is coming.</i></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Evaluation - A time for self-reflection.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Fight for your life.</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight back - It hides in disguises. Different weapons and tools can be used to ward it off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mirror - Use mirrors to affirm that you're still you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Friends(?) - That's new.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Uncover the mysteries of Caelum</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzles - Discover the truth, whether above ground or below.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We had an arrangement - Maybe things will be different this time around.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HAVE YOU HEARD?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/extras/TheChef.png?t=1735394502\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735394502","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/page.bg.jpg?t=1735394502","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/9cdbf9d33570de2d90c501013eb2f2ef39e2f5c5/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735394502","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406060/9cdbf9d33570de2d90c501013eb2f2ef39e2f5c5/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735394502","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Self-harm, child abuse, body mutilation & suicide."},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><str